    <stitle>INTERNATIONAL&#174; VT 365 DIESEL ENGINE - OIL COOLER and FILTER HOUSING - Installation</stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>Installation</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
            <title>Oil Cooler Cover Assembly</title>
            <figure id="f2650916" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figd13/d1381.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="312px" box="no"/>
                <caption>Figure 343. Pump inlet strainer (150 micron)</caption>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install a clean pump inlet strainer to the oil reservoir.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Make sure dirt, sludge or debris does not restrict oil flow from crankcase to the
                    hydraulic oil pump.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Add oil to correct level in oil reservoir.</para>
            </step1>
            <figure id="f2350915" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figd13/d1308.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
                <caption>Figure 344. Oil cooler cover assembly</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Oil cooler cover assembly</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Oil cooler</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Pump inlet strainer</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Reservoir cover gasket</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install a new reservoir cover gasket onto the oil cooler cover assembly.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Lower oil cooler cover assembly onto engine crankcase.</para>
            </step1>
            <figure id="f2050916" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figd13/d1307.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
                <caption>Figure 345. Mounting bolts for oil cooler cover assembly</caption>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install eight M8 x 30, and two M8 x 85 mounting bolts into the oil cooler cover
                    assembly. Tighten mounting bolts to the special torque .
                </para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
